 which his jailed mind kept digging? The recollection of a dream. The warning addressed to him in a dream. A prediction, which up to now had in no way hampered his life, but which at present, at the inexorable approach of a certain deadline, was beginning to sound with an insistent, ever-increasing resonance.

“You must control yourself,” cried Itski to Graf in a hysterical recitative. He cleared his throat and walked to the closed window.

